ed to be\nimpressed with the idea that the stock\ncould be had at lower figures, and the\nbid price fixed for the day at 7.\nOther trading included a few bonds,\nsome railway shares, and odds and ends\namong the bank and insurance stocks.\nLOCAL FINANCIAL GOSSIP.\nWASHINGTON STOCK MARKET.\nBales\u2014Regular call, 12 o'clock noon:\nBales\u2014Regular call, 12 o'clock noon:\nCapital Traction 5s, $.,000 at 118\n4s, $1,000 at\nWashington Gas, 2 at 70%.\nMergenthaler, 10 at 200%, 10 at 20%, 5 at 204,\neom., 2 at 38\nMergenthaler, 1 at 220%,\nWashington Railway and Eleotrio pid., 4 at 8.\nFollowing are the bid and asked prices on yester\nday's Washington Stock Exchange:\nJAS BONDS.\nat 115\nBid.\nWashington Gas $5.....ccccvivreciasnses. 108\nWashington Gas cert, 68.......ccecae0. 105%\nRAILROAD BONDS,\nCapital Traction 5s... sersanmeenenee T1486\nAnacostia and Potomac Baca rovecreserees 2\nGas 5s\nCity and\nTYPE MACHINE 3 STOCKS,\nLanston MODOLYPE ...cisiisisscansirnsanes\nLanston rights seamen AEE EEE EE EE EET)\nMINING Bloons.\nNATIONAL BANK\nVernon...\nSteamboat.\nthi ngton Gas\norgetown Gas.\nis an\n\nGreene\n33\ngh EEESE GESBEENENEIE Lol\nFarmers and Mechanioh.eeesrsmsesacemens 36\nRAROIRE oovuvstessacssinssnsttnanbase suspuns 13\nRespite LLL LLL LL LL 159%\nely teste SEES SA SE SAR ARTI\nTRUST COMPANY STOCKS.\nAmerican Security and Trust..c.c... sees 30\nNational Savings and Trust....... ceasere Sp\nLT RR ERA svsrsnerees 153\nWashington Loan and Trust............. X05\nUnited States Trust.... Rn i\nSAVINGS BANK STOCKS.\nMerchants snd Mechanics... sesrsssnsases 158\nUnion\nHome\nDime\nRRL SPA, RI. mw\nFIRE INSURANCE STOCKS.\nArlington ERE srvens- 3\nCOmMETCIAl \u00ab..covrsrniscineesssestesioscncss\nCORCORAN vsvessrrsstsnnansasstonspsnnssttons 3F\nFirsmen's ........ossesssisn vessssanrestins\nGerpan- diyefioan srisunrsesusasstesassrns BN\nNational Union.. ERLERRARTE A\nIPOROBBAE env sissrnrrrasnrresnasnsssnsiny\nper cc ur months %ady five\nRates, by\n1) bills receiv